order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः स्थापना-२०२३/ प्र.क्र.३४१/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: thalani, T. Regarding sanction of new Primary Health Centre at Hadgaon, District Nanded as a special case.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2023 / Q. No.341 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of the Director, Health Services, Mumbai: Go to No. 7A / Room 7A / T-8 / Frying / Prayake / Establishment / Nanded / 7288-90/2023 Date 27.10.2023.
Introduction: - Mouje fry, Ta. The government was considering sanctioning a new primary health centre at Hadgaon, district Nanded. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - Mouje Fali Ta. New primary health is being approved as a special case in Hadgaon, District Nanded.
This Government decision will be made available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
